data.description: Welcome to this charming Split-Entry home boasting 1486 sqft of comfortable living space located in the heart of Papillion. This delightful home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1 fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. Enjoy the convenience of new ceiling fans and smart lighting, enhancing comfort and efficiency. Indulge in culinary delights with all-new Samsung Bespoke appliances and upgraded kitchen fixtures.  Step onto newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring (LVP).  It is complemented by fresh interior and exterior paint, along with a newly installed water softener system. Situated on a spacious lot, this home offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this your home - schedule a viewing today!
